def evaluate(i):
    start = time.time()
    os.system(FLINKDIR+'/bin/flink run -c '+EVAL_CLASS+' '+JAR+' -in '+inputName(i+1)+' -out '+outputName(i)+' -delim , -model '+modelName(i)+' -learning-rate 0.1 -neg-sample-rate 9 > /dev/null')
    end = time.time()
    day = -1
    inv = 0
    hit = 0
    ndcg = 0.0
    os.system('rm '+OUTPUT_CSV+str(i))
    os.system('touch '+OUTPUT_CSV+str(i))
    with open(outputName(i)) as f:
        for line in f:            
            if 'Period' in line:
                day = int(line[(line.rfind(' ')+1):-1])
            if ':Number of invokes' in line:
                inv = int(line[(line.rfind(' ')+1):-1])
            if ':Avg nDCG' in line:
                ndcg = float(line[(line.rfind(' ')+1):-1])
            if ':Hit' in line:
                hit = int(line[(line.rfind(' ')+1):-1])
                os.system('echo "'+str(day)+','+str(inv)+','+str(ndcg)+','+str(hit/inv)+'" >> '+OUTPUT_CSV+str(i))

    os.system('cat '+outputName(i))

def dailyChart(week):
    data = np.loadtxt(OUTPUT_CSV+str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    data2 = np.loadtxt(OUTPUT_NOLEARN_CSV+str(week), delimiter=',', skiprows=0)
    day = data[:,0]
    inv = data[:,1]
    nDCG = data[:,2]
    hit = data[:,3]
    day2 = data2[:,0]
    inv2 = data2[:,1]
    nDCG2 = data2[:,2]
    hit2 = data2[:,3]
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(221)
    ax2 = fig.add_subplot(222)
    
    ax.set_ylabel('nDCG')
    ax2.set_ylabel('hit')
    
    fig.subplots_adjust(right=0.75)
    
    ax2.set_frame_on(True)
    ax2.patch.set_visible(False)
    
    for i in range(0, min(len(day), len(day2))):
        nDCG2[i] = nDCG2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
        hit2[i] = hit2[i] * inv2[i] / inv[i]
    
    ax.plot(day, nDCG, marker='o', color="Red", label="learning")
    ax.plot(day2, nDCG2, marker='o', color="Magenta", label="no learning")
    ax.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Red")
    
    ax2.plot(day, hit, marker='o', color="Blue", label="learning")
    ax2.plot(day2, hit2, marker='o', color="Cyan", label="no learning")
    ax2.tick_params(axis='y', colors="Blue")
    
    ax.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    ax2.set_xlabel('Day (Week '+str(week)+')')
    
    ax.legend()
    ax2.legend()
    ax.grid()
    ax2.grid
    plt.ylim(0,0.15)
    plt.show()
